These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-1::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  analyst, paramedic, fisherman
1. the paramedic is on the far left##1
2. the analyst is on the right of the fisherman##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |     2     |     3     |
| Job   | paramedic | fisherman | analyst |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-2::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  freelancer, pilot, police-officer
1. the police-officer is on the far right##1
2. the freelancer is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |   2    |      3       |
| Job   | freelancer | pilot | police-officer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-3::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: fishing, woodworking, drawing
1. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far left##1
2. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |      3      |
| Hobby   | fishing | woodworking | drawing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-4::.
There are 3 different nationalities: spanish, german, egyptian
1. the german is on the far right##1
2. the german is on the right of the egyptian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |
| Nationality   | spanish | egyptian | german |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-5::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, lemonade, coffee
1. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
2. the person drinking coffee is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |      2      |   3   |
| Beverage   | lemonade | cola | coffee |

