.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-6::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: scooter, skateboard, bus
1. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
2. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2  |  3   |
| Transport   | bus | skateboard | scooter |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-7::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: scientific, musical, zombie
1. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
2. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |      3       |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie | scientific | musical |

 #################################

 
